public class Effect
extends EffectBase

Defines an effect in place on a combatant during an encounter.

Parameters:
name - the name of the effect
ID - an identifier for the effect (used in Hashtables, etc.)
source - the Combatant.getCombatHandle() of the effect's source
target - the Combatant.getCombatHandle() of the effect's target
roundTill - the round the effect expires
dur - the EffectBase.Duration of the effect
beneficial - true if the effect is beneficial to its target
